title: What time does Strictly Come Dancing start?
text:
What time does Strictly Come Dancing start? By WMNdellis | Posted: October 11, 2015 Claudia and Tess What time does Strictly Come Dancing start? X 
Copy link to paste in your message / 
Which two couples will end up in the nail biting dance off tonight? tune in to find out. 
Last night the celebrities were put through their paces for the movie themed week. 
Tess Daly and Claudia Winkleman host the hit series. 
See which could gets voted off at 7.15pm.
